Package: kdiplo
Title: Korean Diplomacy Data Hub: A One-Stop Public Repository for Datasets on Korean Diplomacy
Version: 0.1.0.9002
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Kadir Jun", 
    family = "Ayhan", 
    email = "k@ayhan.phd", 
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8052-1938")))
Description: Several novel datasets on Korean diplomacy, mainly focusing on high-level diplomatic visits (both outgoing and incoming), their formats (bilateral, multilateral, informal), nature (such as state visits), purposes (economic, security, etc.), timelines, and the conveners in multilateral contexts among others.
